	<ThingDef ParentName="MG_ArmorBase">
		<defName>MG_ZhongArmor</defName>
		<label>蒙兀重甲</label>
		<description>蒙兀人采用神州锻造技术锻造而成的重甲，它的防护性能极佳，虽然穿上去会稍微减缓移动速度，但这对于体格健壮的蒙兀起兵们来说都不是问题\n\n蒙兀士兵们借助这样的盔甲能轻易地击溃那些胆敢冒犯他们的中世纪文明。</description>
		<graphicData>
			<drawSize>1.4</drawSize>
			<texPath>Things/Apparel/MGZhongJia/MGZhongJia</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<recipeMaker>
			<skillRequirements>
				<Crafting>3</Crafting>
			</skillRequirements>
		</recipeMaker>

		<costList>
			<Steel>150</Steel>
		</costList>

		<statBases>
			<MaxHitPoints>200</MaxHitPoints>
			<WorkToMake>15000</WorkToMake>
			<Mass>6</Mass>
			<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.7</ArmorRating_Sharp>
			<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.4</ArmorRating_Blunt>
			<ArmorRating_Heat>0.6</ArmorRating_Heat>
			<Insulation_Cold>3</Insulation_Cold>
			<Insulation_Heat>1</Insulation_Heat>
			<EquipDelay>7</EquipDelay>
		</statBases>

		<equippedStatOffsets>
			<MoveSpeed>-0.1</MoveSpeed>
		</equippedStatOffsets>

		<apparel>
			<bodyPartGroups>
				<li>Torso</li>
				<li>Shoulders</li>
				<li>Arms</li>
				<li>Waist</li>
				<li>Legs</li>
			</bodyPartGroups>
			<wornGraphicPath>Things/Apparel/MGZhongJia/MGZhongJia</wornGraphicPath>
			<layers>
				<li>OnSkin</li>
			</layers>
		</apparel>

	</ThingDef>
	



	<ThingDef ParentName="MG_ArmorBase">
		<defName>MG_QingArmor</defName>
		<label>蒙兀元甲</label>
		<description>蒙兀人采用神州锻造技术锻造而成的轻质盔甲，它的防护性能较好，穿上它后不会影响移动速度，因此它受到了蒙兀族新兵的青睐。\n\n在面对一些威力不大的武器时，它能够有效的抵消来自这些武器的伤害，但面对一些穿甲能力强的武器时，这种盔甲就会略显逊色。</description>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>Things/Apparel/MGQingJia/MGQingJia</texPath>
